These amenities are evenly spread over the whole area with the exception of{ {Castlemilk}which is lacking in most amenities
The grassland, which is mostly used as rough grazing is situated around the village of{Carmunnock}between Stamperland Sheddens and Castlemilk
A river called the{White Cart Water} runs through the centre of the area in a South to North direction to join up with the{River Clyde}in{Glasgow}
To the east of this river there are patches of{deciduous}woodland, the largest expanse of which is on{ {Netherton Braes }
